  [ Frank S. Thomas ]
  * debian/patches/:
    - 01_amd64-disable-platform-reset.dpatch: Only reset projects if the
      platform name in the statefile is not empty. This bugfix has been
      backported from BOINC 5.8. (closes: #407461)

